---
title: Classic Chicken Parmigiana with Garden Salad
description: Why go out for this nostalgic pub classic when you can create it right in your own kitchen? There’s not much to analyse here – just good old-fashioned tasty, gooey chicken parmy. This one's going straight to the pool room!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-parmigiana-4aa219c4.jpg
